description:
With offices in Federal Way and Tacoma, the law firm of Park Chenaur & Associates, Inc., has become one of our region's premier sources for quality, professional and effective advocacy and support to individuals and families throughout the greater Sea-Tac area who are suffering needlessly as the result of someone else's negligence or wrongdoing.

Focusing solely on personal injury and wrongful death claims, our law firm's top-rated, award-winning lawyers are fully prepared to do all we can to increase your chances of obtaining the maximum amount of compensation you deserve. To date, we have secured more than $50 million in verdicts and settlements for our plaintiff clients.

From our law firm's success, we have received hundreds of five-star client reviews on Google and Facebook along with numerous testimonials and referrals from those we have served. Additionally, our attorneys have earned Top 100 Trial Lawyer designations from the National Trial Lawyers along with recognition as being among the Best Personal Injury Attorneys in our area from Expertise.

We have also received many other top rankings and endorsements from our peers, and our law firm has an additional office in Federal Way to provide convenient access to the compassionate, yet aggressive, representation you need.

To find out more about how we can best assist you with your legal challenge and improve the likelihood you will obtain the favorable outcomes you seek, you can schedule a free initial consultation by contacting Park Chenaur & Associates, Inc., by phone or through our website. We also offer virtual consultations so that you do not have to further risk your health and safety to speak with us.
